;W[qs]LB[rs:1][qr:2][qs:3]C[Dia.1 Husu Bik for White

If White plays at the 2,1 point then Black will play at 2 next.  After 2 there pretty much is no continuation.  White will play 3, and Black can take seonsu, so this is a Husu Bik fo White.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

