;W[rs]LB[qr:1][pr:2][rs:3]C[Dia.2 Pae

If you cut at 1 then you're off to a good start.  Black will dansu at 2 and then White can form a Pae with 3.  This is actually the crucial point.  White 3 forms a Pae, when White should be able to capture.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

